                     <msItem xml:id="p1_i1">
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2741RepCh25">Malkǝʾa ḥǝmāmāta masqal</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <note>This <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām</foreign> has 54 stanzas, the
                           following is the first. <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                              <lb/>ሰላም፡ ለሕማምከ፡ ቤተ፡ አይሁድ፡ ዘአመዝበረ። <lb/>ወረሰዮሙ፡ ዝርዙረ። <lb/>ዘሴሬቅ፡ ወይነ፡
                              እምነ፡ ዕጕስታር፡ መረ። <lb/>ተማሕፀነ፡ በሕማምከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ት</supplied>ረ።
                              <lb/>እምአምልኮ፡ ጣዖት፡ አድ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ኅ</supplied>ን፡ ዛቲ፡ ሀገረ።</foreign>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="p1_i2">
                        <locus from="14v"/>
                        <title type="incomplete">Beginning of a <foreign xml:lang="gez">salām</foreign> for the Cross</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
